---
title: Dukkah-Roasted Cauliflower with Lemon Yogurt
description: Sweet and savoury collide in this delicious hearty dish. Roasted cauliflower is a dreamy match for herby, nutty dukkah and the addition of bulgur adds a satisfying chew that is sure to fill you up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dukkah-roasted-cauliflower-7c546aca.jpg
